It's Friday and your weekend starts now! Pause your remote work session and disconnect your Teams session. We might be isolated, but we're in this together. CLIPCast is the new sound of our Community. Featuring music sessions, interviews, debates and mindful moments, CLIPCast is our school at its best. We wanted to create something for the community, by the community. We are together and, regardless of the physical separation, we will keep in touch. You'll hear the familiar voices you miss and be reminded that, more than ever, #WeAreOne. Tune in every Friday for a weekly dose of feel good.
